node.text: "But if we learned anything from sports, is that no matter how far down we may be, we are never too far down to come back."
The Houston-based rapper brings his workwear touch to Nike SB, adding bandana patterns, rope-style fat laces, and more to the fat-tongued gem.

node.text: This upcoming All-Star Weekend in Chicago is sure to be packed with must-have releases. Check out this quick recap of what Jordan, Nike, and Converse have prepared for mid-February.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 29, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says 'AIR JORDAN 1 LOW OG FRAGMENT TRAVIS STEAKERNEWS NEWS'.

node.text: Official images of the fragment design x Travis Scott x Air Jordan 1 Low OG have surfaced ahead of the expected 8/13 release. Hit the link in our bio to see the full images.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 29, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: @undefeatedinc recalls the golden era of exotic materials on sneakers with their Nike Dunk vs. AF-1 "5 On It". Each features five materials (leather, suede, nubuck, canvas, snakeskin), while the five-strikes logo also nods to this latest chapter of their Dunk vs. AF-1 series. An official release is scheduled For August 6th exclusively at Undefeated chapter stores and online; hit the link in our bio for more details.

node.text: Official images of the Nike Dunk Low Scrap "Archaeo Brown" has emerged! The Dunk is completely transformed with a rebuilt aesthetic made to appear as if it was created with scrap material. Tap the link in our bio for a closer look.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on July 29, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: New Balance officially unites with Levi's for a special capsule that embodies the Made In America spirit. Included in the collection is the 992 as well as a set of two-toned denim jeans and jackets. Hit the link in our bio to get a closer look at this upcoming 8/6 drop.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on July 29, 2021 tagging @chriscolgan. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: In-hand look at the upcoming Air Jordan 5 "Oreo" is here! What other Retro drops should @jumpman23 bring back? We nominate the Air Jordan 3 "Do The Right Thing". Tap the link in our bio to get a closer look at the Oreo 5s.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on July 29, 2021 tagging @jimmygorecki. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: @undefeated DUNK vs. AF-1. Which pair wins this round?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sneaker News on July 29, 2021 tagging @yeezymafia. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: The adidas Yeezy 700 v3 "Dark Glow" is set to arrive soon. Featuring glow-in-the-dark exterior cages above a black/grey knit upper, this latest 700 v3 is expected to drop as part of the Yeezy Day festivities on August 2nd. Tap the link in our bioo for more details.

node.text: Nike introduces the Dunk High Rebel, a slightly modified Dunk for women that revisits the "Reimagined" campaign of 2019. While these won't live up to classic model, the Rebel does offer a unique option for women who have skewed toward models like the Air Force 1 Shadow. Tap the link in our bio to get a first look.

node.text: The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 v2 is set to release in "Mauve"; this upcoming drop features a mix of dark neutrals - a common sight in Yeezy footwear. Tap the link in our bio for a closer look.

node.text: So...how many pairs are you going for? Hit the link in our bio to see a detailed look at the upcoming Cool Grey Jordan 11. These are expected to drop on December 11th in full family sizes.
